WEBVTT

NOTE Video ID: DB4Y_PDG8tQ

NOTE Language: en

00:00:08.197 --> 00:00:11.974
Yogi: Shri Mataji, could You please tell us more about Hamsa Chakra?

00:00:12.054 --> 00:00:13.522
Hamsa Chakra?

00:00:14.661 --> 00:00:18.335
Hamsa Chakra is placed here

00:00:18.415 --> 00:00:21.320
where some of the nerves

00:00:21.400 --> 00:00:24.939
which are coming from Ida and Pingala cross over,

00:00:25.019 --> 00:00:31.935
and is a part of Vishuddhi Chakra.

00:00:33.540 --> 00:00:38.111
Plus the connection with Vishuddhi and Agya:

00:00:38.191 --> 00:00:42.818
as you must have read in the Devi Mahatmyam that

00:00:42.898 --> 00:00:47.184
Shri Krishna is the Father of Christ,

00:00:47.264 --> 00:00:51.639
so the connection between the two is maintained here.

00:00:52.560 --> 00:00:55.660
And this is very important, Hamsa Chakra is,

00:00:55.740 --> 00:01:01.233
that if your Hamsa Chakra is not all right, your discretion is very poor.

00:01:02.428 --> 00:01:06.759
This chakra will get easily dried out.

00:01:07.320 --> 00:01:10.676
Like if you eat very dried food, you see.

00:01:10.756 --> 00:01:15.523
Say, sometimes you also offer Me some dried food,

00:01:15.603 --> 00:01:18.855
and I have to tell you that not to give too dry food.

00:01:18.935 --> 00:01:25.640
You must eat it with some sauce or some liquid thing, because if you eat very dry food

00:01:25.720 --> 00:01:27.830
also this becomes very dry.

00:01:28.487 --> 00:01:30.542
And it’s very important

00:01:30.622 --> 00:01:34.093
because if this portion becomes dry,

00:01:34.173 --> 00:01:39.205
you can put some oil or ghee into it to make it all right.

00:01:39.285 --> 00:01:45.530
But from here starts the drying of the peritoneum and the lining.

00:01:46.427 --> 00:01:48.985
If the peritoneum gets dried up,

00:01:49.065 --> 00:01:50.985
the whole body gets dried up.

00:01:51.065 --> 00:01:54.350
It can be anywhere; in the lung if it is dried up

00:01:54.430 --> 00:01:56.671
it can cause you lung cancer.

00:01:56.751 --> 00:02:01.600
As even the peritoneum can be in a cancer state.

00:02:01.680 --> 00:02:05.520
So one has to be very careful not to take something very dry,

00:02:05.600 --> 00:02:09.715
all the time dry food and dry things.

00:02:09.795 --> 00:02:14.815
Moreover, not to put anything to make this a lubricant

00:02:16.120 --> 00:02:21.280
– some sort of a lubricant should be there so there’s no problem on this chakra.

00:02:21.360 --> 00:02:24.872
Because first of all it loses your discretion,

00:02:24.952 --> 00:02:28.629
you don’t understand things, you don’t know what to do. You mean it,

00:02:28.709 --> 00:02:34.801
you mean good, but you don’t do. When you achieve something, it’s something not so good.

00:02:34.881 --> 00:02:37.111
The reason is, your discretion is poor.

00:02:37.191 --> 00:02:40.647
For that this must not be made dry.

00:02:46.552 --> 00:02:48.900
I have told many a times to put some

00:02:48.980 --> 00:02:53.075
ghee every day. Get a little bottle of ghee,

00:02:53.994 --> 00:02:57.305
keep it with you with a little dropper.

00:02:57.385 --> 00:02:59.281
You can put it in the hot water,

00:02:59.361 --> 00:03:05.560
you can heat it up every day, and take two drops in the nose

00:03:05.640 --> 00:03:10.514
in the night and in the morning time. It doesn’t take much, but it should be done.

00:03:11.650 --> 00:03:14.466
It’s for your good.

00:03:17.309 --> 00:03:20.300
That’s the only ritual I think we follow, do we

00:03:20.380 --> 00:03:22.277
– have we any other ritual?

00:03:22.357 --> 00:03:24.776
We don’t even make a cross!